<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.3">
<l>maṭaneñcāṟ kuṟaivillā makaṭṭāycey torupēycci</l>
<l>viṭanañca mulaicuvaitta mikuñāṉac ciṟukuḻavi</l>
<l>paṭanākat taṇaikkiṭanta paruvaraittōḷ parampuruṭa</l>
<l>ṉeṭumāyaṉ kavarāta niṟaiyiṉāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except the want for [our] foolish heart</l>
<l>we have no want for [our] fullness that is not seized by the tall Dark one/trickster,</l>
<l>the highest man with big mountain shoulders who lies on a hooded-cobra bed,</l>
<l>the very insightful small child that tasted the breast with poison to be</l>
	<l>released by a demoness acting as a human mother.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
